data.text:
Philip Urso

//

Co-founder/facilitator at Live Love Teach, a national yoga teacher training school.

Ten years with Baron Baptiste, where, prior to starting Live Live Teach, he rose to Co-Facilitator.

In 2014, co-founded Rhode Island Power Yoga with Renee Deslauriers and Terry Munnelly.

A fluent teacher of A Course in Miracles which also informs his teaching and inspires his coaching.

Philip’s two 5-star podcasts on iTunes — A Crash Course in Miracles and Yoga Classes, Live Love Teach — have millions downloads.

ERYT-500 with over 10,000 teaching hours.
